A playful golden retriever bursting through shattered laboratory glass, trailing colorful interconnected nodes and flowing lines behind it like a dynamic mind map visualization. The dog's movement creates sweeping arcs of luminous connections branching outward in organic patterns. Broken beakers and test tubes scatter in the foreground while holographic tag labels float ethereally without readable text. The scene uses a rich cyberpunk palette of electric blues, hot pinks, and neon greens against a dark industrial lab backdrop with exposed pipes and flickering monitors. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the glowing network streams. The composition captures explosive forward motion and liberation, with the digital mind map tendrils stretching toward the viewer like neural pathways escaping into the world.
